#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:3
msgid "Gmail Plugin"
msgstr "Gmail-plugin"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Gmail Plugin* integrates an Odoo database with a Gmail inbox, so users "
"can keep track of all their work between Gmail and Odoo, without losing any "
"information."
msgstr ""
"*Gmail-pluginet* integrerer en Odoo-database med en Gmail-indbakke, så "
"brugere kan holde styr på alt deres arbejde mellem Gmail og Odoo uden at "
"miste nogen oplysninger."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:9
msgid ""
"Make sure to check the database version in the :menuselection:`Settings app "
"--> General Settings`, at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for at tjekke databaseversionen i :menuselection:`Settings app --> "
"General Settings` nederst på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:12
msgid ""
"For database versions 19.2 and later, see the `latest documentation <https://"
"www.odoo.com/documentation/master/applications/general/integrations/"
"mail_plugins/gmail.html>`_ for installation instructions."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:17
msgid "Odoo Online users"
msgstr "Odoo Online-brugere"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:19
msgid ""
"For databases hosted on Odoo Online (or Odoo.sh), follow the steps below to "
"configure the Gmail Plugin."
msgstr ""
"For databaser hostet på Odoo Online (eller Odoo.sh) skal du følge "
"nedenstående trin for at konfigurere Gmail-pluginet."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:23
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:102
msgid "Install the Gmail Plugin"
msgstr "Installer Gmail-pluginet"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:25
msgid ""
"First, log in to the Gmail account that the user wishes to connect to Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Log først ind på den Gmail-konto, som brugeren ønsker at forbinde til Odoo."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:27
msgid ""
"From the Gmail inbox, click the plus sign icon on the right side panel to "
"get add-ons. If the side panel is not visible, click on the arrow icon at "
"the bottom right corner of the inbox to reveal it."
msgstr ""
"Fra Gmail-indbakken skal du klikke på plusikonet på sidepanelet til højre "
"for at få tilføjelser. Hvis sidepanelet ikke er synligt, skal du klikke på "
"pileikonet nederst i højre hjørne af indbakken for at få det frem."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:None
msgid "Plus sign icon on the Gmail inbox side panel."
msgstr "Plusikon på sidepanelet i Gmail-indbakken."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:34
msgid ""
"Then, use the search bar to search for `Odoo` and locate the :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Inbox Addin`."
msgstr ""
"Brug derefter søgelinjen til at søge efter `Odoo` og find :guilabel:`Odoo "
"Inbox Addin`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:None
msgid "Odoo Inbox Addin on Google Workspace Marketplace."
msgstr "Odoo Inbox Addin på Google Workspace Marketplace."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:40
msgid ""
"Or, go directly to the :guilabel:`Odoo Inbox Addin` page on the `Google "
"Workspace Marketplace <https://workspace.google.com/marketplace/app/"
"odoo_inbox_addin/873497133275>`_."
msgstr ""
"Eller gå direkte til siden for :guilabel:`Odoo Inbox Addin` på `Google "
"Workspace Marketplace <https://workspace.google.com/marketplace/app/"
"odoo_inbox_addin/873497133275>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:43
msgid ""
"Once the plugin is located, click :guilabel:`Install`. Then, "
"click :guilabel:`Continue` to start the installation."
msgstr ""
"Når plugin'et er fundet, skal du klikke på :guilabel:`Install`. Klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`Continue` for at starte installationen."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:46
msgid ""
"Next, select which Gmail account the user wishes to connect to Odoo. Then "
"click :guilabel:`Allow` to let Odoo access the Google account. Google will "
"then show a pop-up window confirming that the installation was successful."
msgstr ""
"Vælg derefter hvilken Gmail-konto brugeren ønsker at forbinde til Odoo. Klik "
"derefter på :guilabel:`Allow` for at give Odoo adgang til Google-kontoen. "
"Google viser derefter et pop op-vindue, der bekræfter, at installationen var "
"vellykket."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:51
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:142
msgid "Configure the Odoo database"
msgstr "Konfigurer Odoo-databasen"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:53
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:144
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Mail Plugin` feature must be enabled in the Odoo database in "
"order to use the Gmail Plugin. To enable the feature, go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings`. Under "
"the :guilabel:`Integrations` section, activate :guilabel:`Mail Plugin`, and "
"then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"Funktionen :guilabel:`Mail Plugin` skal være aktiveret i Odoo-databasen for "
"at kunne bruge Gmail Plugin. For at aktivere funktionen skal du gå til "
":menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings`. Under afsnittet "
":guilabel:`Integrations` skal du aktivere :guilabel:`Mail Plugin` og "
"derefter klikke på :guilabel:`Save`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:None
msgid "The Mail Plugin feature in the Settings."
msgstr "Funktionen Mail Plugin i indstillingerne."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:63
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:153
msgid "Configure the Gmail inbox"
msgstr "Konfigurer Gmail-indbakken"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:65
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:155
msgid ""
"In the Gmail inbox, a purple Odoo icon is now visible on the right side "
"panel. Click on the Odoo icon to open up the Odoo plugin window. Then, click "
"on any email in the inbox. Click :guilabel:`Authorize Access` in the plugin "
"window to grant Odoo access to the Gmail inbox."
msgstr ""
"I Gmail-indbakken er der nu et lilla Odoo-ikon synligt på højre sidepanel. "
"Klik på Odoo-ikonet for at åbne Odoo plugin-vinduet. Klik derefter på en "
"vilkårlig e-mail i indbakken. Klik på :guilabel:`Authorize Access` i plugin-"
"vinduet for at give Odoo adgang til Gmail-indbakken."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:None
msgid ""
"The Authorize Access button in the right sidebar of the Odoo plugin panel."
msgstr "Knappen Authorize Access i højre sidebjælke i Odoo plugin-panelet."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:73
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:163
msgid ""
"Next, click :guilabel:`Login`. Then, enter the URL of the Odoo database that "
"the user wishes to connect to the Gmail inbox, and log in to the database."
msgstr ""
"Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Login`. Indtast derefter URL'en på den Odoo-"
"database, som brugeren ønsker at forbinde til Gmail-indbakken, og log ind på "
"databasen."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:77
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:167
msgid ""
"Use the general URL for the database, not the URL of a specific page in the "
"database. For example, use `https://mycompany.odoo.com`, not `https://"
"mycompany.odoo.com/web#cids=1&action=menu`."
msgstr ""
"Brug den generelle URL for databasen, ikke URL'en for en bestemt side i "
"databasen. Brug f.eks. `https://mycompany.odoo.com`, ikke `https://"
"mycompany.odoo.com/web#cids=1&action=menu`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:81
#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:171
msgid ""
"Finally, click :guilabel:`Allow` to let Gmail access the Odoo database. The "
"browser will then show a :guilabel:`Success!` message. After that, close the "
"window. The Gmail inbox and Odoo database are now connected."
msgstr ""
"Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Allow` for at lade Gmail få adgang til Odoo-"
"databasen. Browseren viser derefter en :guilabel:`Success!`-meddelelse. Luk "
"derefter vinduet. Gmail-indbakken og Odoo-databasen er nu forbundet."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:86
msgid "Odoo On-Premise users"
msgstr "Odoo On-Premise-brugere"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:88
msgid ""
"For databases hosted on servers other than Odoo Online (or Odoo.sh), follow "
"the steps below to configure the Gmail Plugin."
msgstr ""
"For databaser hostet på andre servere end Odoo Online (eller Odoo.sh) skal "
"du følge nedenstående trin for at konfigurere Gmail Plugin."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:92
msgid ""
"As part of their security guidelines, Google requires add-on creators to "
"provide a list of URLs that can be used in actions and redirections launched "
"by the add-on. This protects users by ensuring, for example, that no add-on "
"redirects users toward a malicious website. (Read more on `Google Apps "
"Script <https://developers.google.com/apps-script/manifest/allowlist-url>`_.)"
msgstr ""
"Som en del af deres sikkerhedsretningslinjer kræver Google, at skabere af "
"tilføjelser leverer en liste over URL'er, der kan bruges i handlinger og "
"omdirigeringer, som tilføjelsen udfører. Dette beskytter brugere ved for "
"eksempel at sikre, at ingen tilføjelse omdirigerer brugere til en ondsindet "
"hjemmeside. (Læs mere på `Google Apps Script <https://developers.google.com/"
"apps-script/manifest/allowlist-url>`_.)"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:97
msgid ""
"Since Odoo can only list the `odoo.com` domain and not every on-premise "
"customer's unique server domain, on-premise customers cannot install the "
"Gmail Plugin from the Google Workspace Marketplace."
msgstr ""
"Da Odoo kun kan liste `odoo.com`-domænet og ikke hver enkelt on-premise-"
"kundes unikke serverdomæne, kan on-premise-kunder ikke installere Gmail "
"Plugin fra Google Workspace Marketplace."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:104
msgid ""
"First, access the `GitHub repository <https://github.com/odoo/mail-client-"
"extensions>`_ for the Odoo Mail Plugins. Next, click on the "
"green :guilabel:`Code` button. Then, click :guilabel:`Download ZIP` to "
"download the Mail Plugin files onto the user's computer."
msgstr ""
"Få først adgang til `GitHub-repositoryet <https://github.com/odoo/mail-"
"client-extensions>`_ for Odoo Mail Plugins. Klik derefter på den grønne "
":guilabel:`Code`-knap. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Download ZIP` for at "
"downloade Mail Plugin-filerne til brugerens computer."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:None
msgid "Download the ZIP file from the Odoo GitHub repository for Mail Plugins."
msgstr "Download ZIP-filen fra Odoo GitHub-repositoryet for Mail Plugins."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:112
msgid ""
"Open the ZIP file on the computer. Then, go to :menuselection:`mail-client-"
"extensions-master --> gmail --> src --> views`, and open "
"the :file:`login.ts` file using any text editor software, such as Notepad "
"(Windows), TextEdit (Mac), or Visual Studio Code."
msgstr ""
"Åbn ZIP-filen på computeren. Gå derefter til :menuselection:`mail-client-"
"extensions-master --> gmail --> src --> views`, og åbn filen "
":file:`login.ts` ved hjælp af et tekstredigeringsprogram, såsom Notesblok "
"(Windows), TextEdit (Mac) eller Visual Studio Code."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:116
msgid ""
"Delete the following three lines of text from the :file:`login.ts` file:"
msgstr "Slet følgende tre tekstlinjer fra filen :file:`login.ts`:"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:124
msgid ""
"This removes the `odoo.com` domain constraint from the Gmail Plugin program."
msgstr ""
"Dette fjerner domænebegrænsningen for `odoo.com` fra Gmail Plugin-programmet."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:126
msgid ""
"Next, in the ZIP file, go to :menuselection:`mail-client-extensions-master --"
"> gmail`, and open the file called :guilabel:`appsscript.json`. In "
"the :guilabel:`urlFetchWhitelist` section, replace all the references to "
"`odoo.com` with the Odoo customer's unique server domain."
msgstr ""
"Gå derefter i ZIP-filen til :menuselection:`mail-client-extensions-"
"master --> gmail`, og åbn filen :guilabel:`appsscript.json`. I sektionen "
":guilabel:`urlFetchWhitelist` skal du erstatte alle referencer til "
"`odoo.com` med kundens unikke Odoo-serverdomæne."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:130
msgid ""
"Then, in the same :guilabel:`gmail` folder, open the file "
"called :guilabel:`README.md`. Follow the instructions in "
"the :guilabel:`README.md` file to push the Gmail Plugin files as a Google "
"Project."
msgstr ""
"Åbn derefter i den samme mappe :guilabel:`gmail` filen "
":guilabel:`README.md`. Følg instruktionerne i filen :guilabel:`README.md` "
"for at pushe Gmail Plugin-filerne som et Google-projekt."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:134
msgid ""
"The computer must be able to run Linux commands in order to follow the "
"instructions on the :guilabel:`README.md` file."
msgstr ""
"Computeren skal kunne køre Linux-kommandoer for at følge instruktionerne i "
"filen :guilabel:`README.md`."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/gmail.rst:137
msgid ""
"After that, share the Google Project with the Gmail account that the user "
"wishes to connect to Odoo. Then, click :guilabel:`Publish` "
"and :guilabel:`Deploy from manifest`. Lastly, click :guilabel:`Install the "
"add-on` to install the Gmail Plugin."
msgstr ""
"Del derefter Google-projektet med den Gmail-konto, som brugeren ønsker at "
"forbinde til Odoo. Klik derefter på :guilabel:`Publish` og :guilabel:`Deploy "
"from manifest`. Klik til sidst på :guilabel:`Install the add-on` for at "
"installere Gmail Plugin."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:3
msgid "Outlook Plugin"
msgstr "Outlook-plugin"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:5
msgid ""
"Outlook allows for third-party applications to connect in order to execute "
"database actions from emails. Odoo has a plugin for Outlook that allows for "
"the creation of an opportunity from the email panel."
msgstr ""
"Outlook tillader tredjepartsapplikationer at oprette forbindelse for at "
"udføre databasehandlinger fra e-mails. Odoo har et plugin til Outlook, som "
"gør det muligt at oprette en salgsmulighed fra e-mailpanelet."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:10
msgid ""
"The Outlook plugin is available for both the desktop and web versions of "
"Outlook. See `Microsoft's add-in article <https://support.microsoft.com/en-"
"us/office/use-add-ins-in-outlook-1ee261f9-49bf-4ba6-b3e2-2ba7bcab64c8>`_."
msgstr ""
"Outlook-pluginet er tilgængeligt til både desktop- og webversioner af "
"Outlook. Se `Microsofts artikel om tilføjelser <https://"
"support.microsoft.com/en-us/office/use-add-ins-in-outlook-1ee261f9-49bf-4ba6-"
"b3e2-2ba7bcab64c8>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:17
msgid ""
"The Outlook :doc:`Mail Plugin <../mail_plugins>` needs to be configured both "
"on Odoo and Outlook."
msgstr ""
"Outlook :doc:`Mail Plugin <../mail_plugins>` skal konfigureres både i Odoo "
"og Outlook."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:20
msgid ""
"Make sure to check the database version in the :guilabel:`Settings app --> "
"General Settings`, at the bottom of the page."
msgstr ""
"Sørg for at kontrollere databaseversionen i :guilabel:`Indstillinger-"
"appen --> Generelle indstillinger`, nederst på siden."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:23
msgid ""
"For database versions 19.2 and later, see the `latest documentation <https://"
"www.odoo.com/documentation/master/applications/general/integrations/"
"mail_plugins/outlook.html>`_ for installation instructions."
msgstr ""
"For databaseversioner 19.2 og senere, se `seneste dokumentation <https://"
"www.odoo.com/documentation/master/applications/general/integrations/"
"mail_plugins/outlook.html>`_ for installationsinstruktioner."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:30
msgid "Enable Mail Plugin"
msgstr "Aktivér mail-plugin"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:32
msgid ""
"First, enable the *Mail Plugin* feature in the database. Go "
"to :menuselection:`Settings --> General Settings --> Integrations`, "
"enable :guilabel:`Mail Plugin`, and :guilabel:`Save` the configuration."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:38
msgid "Install the Outlook Plugin"
msgstr "Installér Outlook-plugin"

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:40
msgid ""
"Download (:menuselection:`Save Page As --> Web Page XML only`) the following "
"XML file to upload later: `https://download.odoocdn.com/plugins/outlook/"
"manifest.xml <https://download.odoocdn.com/plugins/outlook/manifest.xml>`_."
msgstr ""
"Download (:menuselection:`Gem side som --> Kun webside XML`) følgende XML-"
"fil til senere upload: `https://download.odoocdn.com/plugins/outlook/"
"manifest.xml <https://download.odoocdn.com/plugins/outlook/manifest.xml>`_."

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:44
msgid ""
"Next, open the Outlook mailbox, and select any email. After completing this, "
"click on the :guilabel:`More actions` button in the upper right-side and "
"select :guilabel:`Get Add-ins`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:None
msgid "More actions button in Outlook"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/general/integrations/mail_plugins/outlook.rst:52
msgid ""
"For locally installed versions of Microsoft Outlook, access "
"the :guilabel:`Get Add-ins` menu item while in preview mode (**not** with a "
"message open). First, click on the :guilabel:`... (ellipsis)` icon in the "
