#: ../../content/applications/general/users/google.rst:3
msgid "Google Sign-In Authentication"
msgstr "Google Sign-In-godkendelse"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/google.rst:5
msgid ""
"The *Google Sign-In Authentication* is a useful function that allows Odoo "
"users to sign in to their database with their Google account."
msgstr ""
"*Google Sign-In-godkendelsen* er en nyttig funktion, der giver Odoo-brugere "
"mulighed for at logge ind på deres database med deres Google-konto."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/google.rst:8
msgid ""
"This is particularly helpful if the organization uses Google Workspace, and "
"wants employees within the organization to connect to Odoo using their "
"Google Accounts."
msgstr ""
"Dette er særligt nyttigt, hvis organisationen bruger Google Workspace og "
"ønsker, at medarbejdere i organisationen kan oprette forbindelse til Odoo "
"ved hjælp af deres Google-konti."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/google.rst:12
msgid ""
"Databases hosted on Odoo.com should not use Oauth login for the owner or "
"administrator of the database as it would unlink the database from their "
"Odoo.com account. If Oauth is set up for that user, the database will no "
"longer be able to be duplicated, renamed or otherwise managed from the "
"Odoo.com portal."
msgstr ""
"Databaser hostet på Odoo.com bør ikke bruge Oauth-login til ejeren eller "
"administratoren af databasen, da det vil fjerne databasens tilknytning til "
"deres Odoo.com-konto. Hvis Oauth er konfigureret for den pågældende bruger, "
"vil databasen ikke længere kunne duplikeres, omdøbes eller på anden måde "
"administreres fra Odoo.com-portalen."

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/google.rst:19
msgid ":doc:`../email_communication/google_oauth`"
msgstr ":doc:`../email_communication/google_oauth`"

#: ../../content/applications/general/users/google.rst:26
msgid ""
"The integration of the Google sign-in function requires configuration both "
"on Google *and* Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Integrationen af Google sign-in-funktionen kræver konfiguration både på "
"Google *og* Odoo."

